{"type": "article", "id": 30279, "title": "户外葡萄酒杯", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-28T23:01:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160728181336d9GkjbEcyxtRYWns.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>谁说在户外喝葡萄酒只能用难看的野营杯或者是脆弱的塑料杯？这款名为 <a href=\"http://www.parqerglass.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Parqer glass</a> 的酒杯可以让人在户外也能保持优雅姿势品味美酒。它上半部分的造型和传统葡萄酒杯无异，下半部分则用一根铝制金属钉代替，可以插入任何柔软的基质当中，适用于各种不同的户外环境。Parqer 的外盒采用了圆柱形的设计，不仅紧凑防震也便于携带。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.parqerglass.com/shop/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 29.90 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160728181354U7TyjNf5aiVJKpDd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.810513\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607281813543cHptlb1LYNUIFTr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.709046\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160728181354JfFWopMnl3gKOBAT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160728181355E2tBO49Yb3FcdfRI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706601\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}